overview: Here at CF, an attentive and hands-on freshmen orientation is mandatory, and in this third volume of out Fresh-Face Freshman series, we're happy to present Colby, Levi, Dylan, Mario learning the ropes. These boys really come out of their shells when our hunky upperclassmen put them through their paces! Our young, inexperienced freshmen are fast learners when it comes to taking big cocks in every position imaginable and their eager to show you that they can keep up just as well as our veterans.
title: Fresh-Faced Freshmen 3
